   },
   "source": [
    "### Stage 6 : Modeling  \n",
    "'Collaborative' or 'User-User' filtering"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "button": false,
    "deletable": true,
    "new_sheet": false,
    "run_control": {
     "read_only": false
    }
   },
   "source": [
    "This technique uses other users to recommend items to the input user. It attempts to find users that have similar preferences and opinions as the input and then recommends items that they have liked to the input. \n",
    "To find similar users we use Pearson Correlation Function\n",
    "\n",
    "The process for creating a User Based recommendation system is as follows:\n",
    "1. Select a user with the movies the user has watched\n",
    "2. Based on his rating to movies, find the top X neighbours \n",
    "3. Get the watched movie record of the user for each neighbour.\n",
    "4. Calculate a similarity score using some formula\n",
    "5. Recommend the items with the highest score\n",
    "\n",
    "Note: Follow the naming convention in movies titles: capital letters, if a movie starts with a \"The\" , like \"The Matrix\" then write it in like this: 'Matrix, The' .  \n",
    "\n",
    "**Creating an input user:**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {
    "button": false,
    "collapsed": false,
    "deletable": true,
    "jupyter": {
     "outputs_hidden": false
    },
    "new_sheet": false,
    "run_control": {
     "read_only": false
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<div>\n",
       "<style scoped>\n",
       "    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n",
       "        vertical-align: middle;\n",
       "    }\n",
       "\n",
       "    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n",
       "        vertical-align: top;\n",
       "    }\n",
       "\n",
       "    .dataframe thead th {\n",
       "        text-align: right;\n",
       "    }\n",
       "</style>\n",
       "<table border=\"1\" class=\"dataframe\">\n",
       "  <thead>\n",
       "    <tr style=\"text-align: right;\">\n",
       "      <th></th>\n",
